クラス AbstractTreeIteratorHandler

  • java.lang.Object

      • org.eclipse.jgit.pgm.opt.AbstractTreeIteratorHandler

  • public class AbstractTreeIteratorHandler
extends org.kohsuke.args4j.spi.OptionHandler<AbstractTreeIterator>
    Custom argument handler AbstractTreeIterator from string values.

    Assumes the parser has been initialized with a Repository.
